    public interface IDiagnosticOperationCycleNeeds
extends IEntity, IDiagnosticCapabilityElement
    IDiagnosticOperationCycleNeeds: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents the needs of a software-component to provide information regarding the operation cycle management to the Dem module.
